The directory agent/lib/ag_ui_strands_patched/ contains a modified version of
the ag-ui-strands package (v0.1.0). Modifications include: ToolBehavior
configuration, session_manager_provider, tools_provider, predict_state
mappings, custom_result_handler, and client_proxy_tool.py for frontend tool
forwarding.

